Provisional mirroring registration for BANC (lanmarks+thin plate splines)

Source: R/data.R
mirror_banc_lm.Rd

This is calibrated in nm. See data-raw/mirror_banc.R for details of how it was generated. It is still provisional pending synpase cloud-based registrations.

Usage

mirror_banc_lm

Format

An object of class tpsreg of length 2.

Examples

utils::str(mirror_banc_lm)
#> List of 2
#>  $ refmat: num [1:58, 1:3] 489926 560133 510763 517672 597499 ...
#>   ..- attr(*, "dimnames")=List of 2
#>   .. ..$ : NULL
#>   .. ..$ : chr [1:3] "X" "Y" "Z"
#>  $ tarmat: num [1:58, 1:3] 410701 473970 511045 491923 433686 ...
#>   ..- attr(*, "dimnames")=List of 2
#>   .. ..$ : NULL
#>   .. ..$ : chr [1:3] "X" "Y" "Z"
#>  - attr(*, "class")= chr "tpsreg"
